How To Build Nyquist on Mac OS X

The project file is based on nyquist/Makefile.
It expects to find the main nyquist directory at ..

To build Nyquist or NyquistIDE:
Open Nyquist Project.pbproj in Project Builder
Set the active target to "Nyquist" or "NyquistIDE"
Click on "build active target"
ny or NyquistIDE will be produced in MacOSXProject/build/

The NyquistIDE.app executable will contain a copy of the ny executable, the runtime directory, and the lib directory.